      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/ml-surrogate-holdout-performance",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Neural network surrogate holdout-set performance",
      "description": "The feedforward neural network surrogate was trained on 4 200 CFD-derived shear-exposure records (single training run, random seed fixed to 42 for reproducibility). Holdout-set evaluation on 1 050 withheld records yielded mean absolute error MAE = 0.0031 RH units and R² = 0.974 against CFD ground truth. The model correctly ranked the worst-case operating point (3.5 L/min, 3 500 RPM) in 100% of holdout cases. Reproducibility was studied informally during development; no ensemble or multi-seed variance statistics are included in this report.",
      "metricName": "MAE / R²",
      "metricValue": "MAE=0.0031; R²=0.974",
      "evidenceSource": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-cbp-cfd-shear-histories-test"
