    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. CFD-experimental agreement (mean 8.3% error) is within the 15% acceptance threshold. The ML surrogate achieves R² = 0.974 on the holdout set and correctly identifies the worst-case operating point. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The combined CFD+ML pipeline is judged credible for the intended COU decision.",
